<hr>
<p>=F0=9F=91=89 So:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>FIFO</strong> =3D easy but may be bad (Belady=E2=80=99s Anomaly)=
.</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>LRU</strong> =3D good practical choice.</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Optimal</strong> =3D benchmark only.</p></li>
</ul>
