<h1 id=3D"OperatingSystem-=F0=9F=94=B9FIFO(First-In-First-Out)PageReplaceme=
nt">=F0=9F=94=B9 FIFO (First-In-First-Out) Page Replacement</h1>
<p>=F0=9F=93=8C <strong>Reference String:</strong> <code>7, 0, 1, 2, 0, 3, =
0, 4</code><br>
=F0=9F=93=8C <strong>Number of Frames:</strong> <code>3</code><br>
=F0=9F=93=8C <strong>Rule:</strong> Always replace the <strong>oldest loade=
d page</strong>.<br>
=F0=9F=93=8C <strong>Data Structure Used:</strong> Queue (First-In =E2=86=
=92 First-Out).</p>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"OperatingSystem-=E2=9C=85Step-by-StepExecution">=E2=9C=85 Step-by=
-Step Execution</h2>
<p>We will track:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>The <strong>state of frames</strong> after each reference</p></li>
<li>
<p>Whether a <strong>page fault</strong> occurs</p></li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"OperatingSystem-Step1:Reference=3D7">Step 1: Reference =3D 7</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Frames are empty =E2=86=92 load <code>7</code></p></li>
<li>
<p>Page Fault =E2=9C=85</p></li>
</ul>
<p>=F0=9F=91=89 Frames: <code>[7]</code><br>
=F0=9F=91=89 Faults so far: <strong>1</strong></p>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"OperatingSystem-Step2:Reference=3D0">Step 2: Reference =3D 0</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p><code>0</code> not in frames =E2=86=92 load <code>0</code></p></li>
<li>
<p>Page Fault =E2=9C=85</p></li>
</ul>
<p>=F0=9F=91=89 Frames: <code>[7, 0]</code><br>
=F0=9F=91=89 Faults so far: <strong>2</strong></p>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"OperatingSystem-Step3:Reference=3D1">Step 3: Reference =3D 1</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p><code>1</code> not in frames =E2=86=92 load <code>1</code></p></li>
<li>
<p>Page Fault =E2=9C=85</p></li>
</ul>
<p>=F0=9F=91=89 Frames: <code>[7, 0, 1]</code><br>
=F0=9F=91=89 Faults so far: <strong>3</strong></p>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"OperatingSystem-Step4:Reference=3D2">Step 4: Reference =3D 2</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p><code>2</code> not in frames =E2=86=92 <strong>replace oldest</strong> (=
which is <code>7</code>)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Page Fault =E2=9C=85</p></li>
</ul>
<p>=F0=9F=91=89 Frames: <code>[2, 0, 1]</code><br>
=F0=9F=91=89 Faults so far: <strong>4</strong></p>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"OperatingSystem-Step5:Reference=3D0">Step 5: Reference =3D 0</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p><code>0</code> <strong>already in frames</strong> =E2=86=92 No fault =E2=
=9D=8C</p></li>
</ul>
<p>=F0=9F=91=89 Frames: <code>[2, 0, 1]</code><br>
=F0=9F=91=89 Faults so far: <strong>4</strong></p>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"OperatingSystem-Step6:Reference=3D3">Step 6: Reference =3D 3</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p><code>3</code> not in frames =E2=86=92 replace oldest (<code>0</code> is=
 not oldest, <code>1</code> is not oldest, <code>0</code><strong> was used =
but oldest in FIFO is </strong><code>0</code><strong> or </strong><code>1</=
code><strong>?</strong>)<br>
=F0=9F=91=89 Careful: In FIFO, order of arrival matters.</p></li>
</ul>
<p>Order of arrival so far: <code>2 (came at step 4), 0 (step 2), 1 (step 3=
)</code><br>
So oldest is <strong>0</strong>.</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Replace <code>0</code> with <code>3</code></p></li>
<li>
<p>Page Fault =E2=9C=85</p></li>
</ul>
<p>=F0=9F=91=89 Frames: <code>[2, 3, 1]</code><br>
=F0=9F=91=89 Faults so far: <strong>5</strong></p>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"OperatingSystem-Step7:Reference=3D0">Step 7: Reference =3D 0</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p><code>0</code> not in frames =E2=86=92 replace oldest</p></li>
</ul>
<p>Order of arrival now: <code>2 (step 4), 1 (step 3), 3 (step 6)</code><br=
>
=F0=9F=91=89 Oldest =3D <code>1</code></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Replace <code>1</code> with <code>0</code></p></li>
<li>
<p>Page Fault =E2=9C=85</p></li>
</ul>
<p>=F0=9F=91=89 Frames: <code>[2, 3, 0]</code><br>
=F0=9F=91=89 Faults so far: <strong>6</strong></p>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"OperatingSystem-Step8:Reference=3D4">Step 8: Reference =3D 4</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p><code>4</code> not in frames =E2=86=92 replace oldest</p></li>
</ul>
<p>Order of arrival now: <code>2 (step 4), 3 (step 6), 0 (step 7)</code><br=
>
=F0=9F=91=89 Oldest =3D <code>2</code></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Replace <code>2</code> with <code>4</code></p></li>
<li>
<p>Page Fault =E2=9C=85</p></li>
</ul>
<p>=F0=9F=91=89 Frames: <code>[4, 3, 0]</code><br>
=F0=9F=91=89 Faults so far: <strong>7</strong></p>
