<h2 id=3D"OperatingSystem-=F0=9F=94=B9FinalResult">=F0=9F=94=B9 Final Resul=
t</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Total References:</strong> 8</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Total Page Faults:</strong> <strong>7</strong> (not 6 =E2=86=92 =
detailed calculation shows <strong>7</strong>).</p></li>
</ul>
