<h2 id=3D"OperatingSystem-ShortexplanationwhyFIFOdidworsehere">Short explan=
ation why FIFO did worse here</h2>
<p>FIFO evicted pages solely by arrival time. At step 6, FIFO evicted <code=
>0</code> (which was needed again soon at step 7), causing an extra fault a=
t step 7. LRU/Optimal preserved <code>0</code> and avoided that extra fault=
.</p>
