<p>=E2=9C=85 <strong>Key Concept:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Hardware provides the device</strong>, <strong>software controls=
 it</strong>, and <strong>OS manages all I/O efficiently</strong>.</p></li>
</ul>
