<h3 id=3D"OperatingSystem-SafetyAlgorithmExecution"><strong>Safety Algorith=
m Execution</strong></h3>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Work =3D (3,3,2), Finish =3D (false, false, false, false, false)</p></li=
>
</ol>
<ul>
<li>
<p>P1 Need =3D (1,2,2) =E2=89=A4 Work =E2=86=92 Yes =E2=86=92 Allocate =E2=
=86=92 Work =3D (5,3,2), Finish[1]=3Dtrue</p></li>
<li>
<p>P3 Need =3D (0,1,1) =E2=89=A4 Work =E2=86=92 Yes =E2=86=92 Work =3D (7,4=
,3), Finish[3]=3Dtrue</p></li>
<li>
<p>P4 Need =3D (4,3,1) =E2=89=A4 Work =E2=86=92 Yes =E2=86=92 Work =3D (7,4=
,5), Finish[4]=3Dtrue</p></li>
<li>
<p>P0 Need =3D (7,4,3) =E2=89=A4 Work =E2=86=92 Yes =E2=86=92 Work =3D (7,5=
,5), Finish[0]=3Dtrue</p></li>
<li>
<p>P2 Need =3D (6,0,0) =E2=89=A4 Work =E2=86=92 Yes =E2=86=92 Work =3D (10,=
5,7), Finish[2]=3Dtrue</p></li>
</ul>
<p>All processes finish =E2=9C=85 =E2=86=92 Safe State.</p>
<p><strong>Safe Sequence =3D P1 =E2=86=92 P3 =E2=86=92 P4 =E2=86=92 P0 =E2=
=86=92 P2</strong></p>
<hr>
<h1 id=3D"OperatingSystem-=F0=9F=94=B9Conclusion">=F0=9F=94=B9 <strong>Conc=
lusion</strong></h1>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Banker=E2=80=99s Algorithm ensures deadlock never happens</stron=
g> by always keeping the system in a <strong>safe state</strong>.</p></li>
<li>
<p>It can be expensive because safety check runs often, but it=E2=80=99s ef=
fective.</p></li>
</ul>
